&lt;p&gt;You’ll work cross-functionally with Procurement, Technology, Marketing, Compliance, and Insurance teams to help Hippo grow responsibly and efficiently in a highly regulated P&amp;amp;C environment. This is an individual contributor role for someone who enjoys owning their work, improving systems, and operating close to the business.&lt;/p&gt;
